<newsItemPage guid="67fb5e37-fb73-43d7-a985-90dfde741a32" id="24758" nodeName="We're all going on a ski holiday" isDoc="" updated="2021-01-20T15:53:04.4970000Z" parentGUID="ee90910d-0178-449a-8ae1-3c4225a1c9d5" nodeTypeAlias="newsItemPage" templateAlias="NewsItemPage" sortOrder="3" published="false" isBlueprint="false">
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>There’s nothing better for quality family time than a <a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">ski trip</a> and therefore Inghams have opened <a data-udi="umb://document/5c6f2f5dfa2c4004b3e082a734fe1507" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c6f2f5dfa2c4004b3e082a734fe1507}" title="Accommodation Options">chalets</a> to allow more groups with children to book.</p>
<p><strong>Sample packages</strong><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Méribel</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a>- Inghams is offering 7 nights, chalet catering at the 4 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/341a80e90ff04d6db0a4d5e3d1f8d4ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/341a80e90ff04d6db0a4d5e3d1f8d4ac}" title="Chalet Camarine">Chalet Camarine</a> Méribel from £2246 based on a family of four (two adults, two children sharing) departing 16th December 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick and resort transfers for the whole family. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13052354/chalet.jpeg" alt="Lakes &amp; Mountains 2016" /></div>
<div style="height: 15px; font-size: x-small; text-align: center;">Chalet Camarine Meribel.</div>
<div> </div>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/4fb215d0c5bf48a09eae325fb09985f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4fb215d0c5bf48a09eae325fb09985f3}" title="Soll">Soll</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a>- Inghams is offering 7 nights chalet catering at the 3 diamond Chalet Bichler, <a data-udi="umb://document/4fb215d0c5bf48a09eae325fb09985f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4fb215d0c5bf48a09eae325fb09985f3}" title="Soll">Söll</a>, Austria from £2715 based on a family of four sharing (2 adults, 2 children), departing 25th February 2017. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick and resort transfers for the whole family. For more information or to book visit www.inghams.co.uk or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13052347/austira_ski-welt-ski-area_soll_chalet-bichler.jpg" alt="Lakes &amp; Mountains 2016" rel="486,273" /></div>
<div style="height: 15px; font-size: x-small; text-align: center;">Chalet Bichler, Soll.</div>
<div> </div>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0}" title="Serre Chevalier">Serre Chevalier</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a>- Inghams is offering 7 nights chalet catering at the 3.5 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/6bd8885963e54918880dd3179e930e08" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6bd8885963e54918880dd3179e930e08}" title="Chalet Pyrene">Chalet Pyrene</a>, Serre Chevalier, France from £2574 based on a family of four (two adults, two children), departing 25th March 2017. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick and resort resort transfers for the whole family. For more information or to book visit www.inghams.co.uk or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13052366/france_serre-chevalier_chalet-pyrene-exterior.jpg" alt="Lakes &amp; Mountains 2016" /></div>
<div style="height: 15px; font-size: x-small; text-align: center;">Chalet Pyrene, Serre Chevalier.</div>
<div> </div>
